
* install git
apt install git

install chrome (download from website)
install libappindicator3-1
install dashlane
ublock origin chrome
ublock origin firefox
add key for bitbucket
* get ubuntu repo:
git clone git@bitbucket.org:gsej/ubuntu-setup.git



get slack from https://slack.com/intl/en-gb/downloads/linux?eu_nc=1
login with domain londoncs.slack.com

download gitgraken from https://www.gitkraken.com/download/linux-deb

download rider from jetbrains.com
expand in ~/bin/
add link to ~/bin/jetbrains.sh

download nordvpn from https://nordvpn.com/download/


run initial.sh
run development.sh
run apps.sh
run docker.sh
run dotnetcore.sh
run install-node.sh

kubuntu configuration
---------------------

* switch to icons-only task manager

* system tray icons
right click on system tray and configure
disable clipboard

* irritating feature that zooms out when selecting an app with multiple instances is:
Desktop Behavior | Desktop Effects | Present Windows

* wallpapers

* notification sounds
Configure audio volume | Applications | Click speaker button

* change login screen image
search for Login Screen SDDM

* switch to zsh:
chsh -s $(which zsh)

* install oh my zsh:
wget https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh/raw/master/tools/install.sh -O - | zsh


to find out:
reduce time of boot loader




